The Mysterious Infecticon watched Transmutate fall and stood there now saying 
a word. He then looked to the surrounding Autobots as he let out a chuckle. 
He then looked to the sky and saw prowl, recognizing him as the Maximal 
leader from the data they recieved from Blacknightmare.

????: "So the Maximal leader is returning. This should be interesting...."

Back in the undersea Base, Frostbite sends a transmission to those who 
requested an alliance.

Frostbite: "Our leader has stepped out for a few moments... he'll return your 
call shortly."
